desc: #momentsofreset is a place of healing where you can find and share Mindful Kits that help you and your loved ones heal and navigate through #MomentsOfReset. Every kit comes with Coach Pav’s "Because I Care" card, a curated quick practice to help kickstart the healing process. We live by our mantra #BecauseICare"
